name: Stars Automatism 8 Variants Crossfade Animation
description: Perhaps folk art-like stylized binary star and background stars, in 8 color variants. This animation slowly crossfades aesthetic pairs. Created in ArtRage, composited and with color variations made in Photoshop. Watercolor and batik-like effects via Filter Forge. Variants are original fire-colored stars, sepia/chocolatey, oceanic (deep blue), gray light on dark and dark on light, dark rose, medium vibrant rose, and light dirty green. By earthbound http://earthbound.io
